  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have spoken-- the first group in Denver was a Catholic grade school, Saint Theresa's in Aurora, Colorado.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These kids had as an assignment the reading of And I went out there that day to a Catholic grade school, and it was one of the most rewarding I've ever given.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those kids kept me all during their lunch hour with the nuns and the other teachers, asking questions.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have spoken over these years to middle schools, high schools, colleges, universities, professional organizations-- the National Court Reporters Association had me do their showcase in 1991 at the New York Hilton to over 1,000 people, including New York judges-- and bar associations, a lot of service organizations-- Lions, Kiwanis, Optimist, and I'm a member of the Optimist Club out here, such organizations, and reporters-- regional conventions, and the United States Air Force Academy, which to me, was a very important one on three occasions, now.",
      "word_count": 86
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In 1994-- especially have I been doing-- asked to do presentations during Holocaust Awareness Week.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I learned in Colorado that-- I think Governor Lamm began that in 1983 after my experience with Carter in Congress setting this up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So 1994, I received an invitation to do the very first Holocaust Awareness Week program at the United States Air Force Academy to-- first to the 89 officers, to the 89 officers.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they-- they were all men, with the exception of about four women, colonels, officers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I finished that day with my slides and the presentation that I give, there was an instant standing ovation, which really moved me, these, you know, people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they called me immediately to present to the cadets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that-- the first speech was in April.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I spoke to the cadets down there on May 10th.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
